messages.message: Need to update our docs with this sort of Flow within the next few hours so any help would be greatly appreciated!
hey Aaron, whats this for? Having 1:1 record:file has come up a lot in my experience as well
Hey Aaron what’s your specific ask here? Can ask others for help, just not sure what they need to do
I think we are all set here! Basically they want to take in a set of CSVs, and the output should be IBOCR files, each with a single record, where each record is a row/line from the CSVs
gotcha i see — btw make sure to use ParsedIBOCR if you want to have this Apply UDF step with continued support
